    - "Wave 643 (uu2941): __neg__, __pos__, __abs__ dict-presence checks for uuid types."
    - "uuid.UUID is an immutable identifier class; uuid.SafeUUID is an IntEnum — neither defines unary negation, positive, or absolute value operators."
